Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,眼見並不為實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seeing is not believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的感官會誤導我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our senses can deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這些星星並不是我們看到的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the stars are not what they appear to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,通過科學展示出的宇宙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cosmos, as revealed by science,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,比我們所能想像的更離奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is stranger than we ever could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,光 時間 空間 萬有引力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Light and time and space and gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,共同創造出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}conspire to create realities
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從未體驗過的現實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which lie beyond human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們一探究竟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,1802年 像這樣的一個夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back in 1802, on a night like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,天文學家威廉·赫歇爾和他的兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the astronomer William Herschel strolled the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在英國海邊散步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the English coast, with his son John.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,赫歇爾是有史以來第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Herschel was the first person ever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}恆星天文學之父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看穿宇宙深層奧秘的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to see into the deeper waters of the cosmic ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他看穿了光線和時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There he glimpsed the magic trick
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一起變出的戲法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that light does with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信有鬼魂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you believe in ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, yes, my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我真沒想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would not have thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是人死後的鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, not in the human kind of ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不是那種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No... not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抬頭看 兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But look up, my boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天空中滿是鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and see a sky full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,星星  父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The stars, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒聽懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,每個星星都像我們的太陽那麼亮 那麼大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every star is a sun as big, as bright as our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看要把太陽移到多遠以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just imagine how far away from us you'd have to move the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,才能讓它看上去像星星那樣小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make it appear as small and faint as a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,星星發出的光 速度很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The light from the stars travels very fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最快的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}faster than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但並不是無限的快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but not infinitely fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,星光到達我們這裏需要時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It takes time for their light to reach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最近的可能需要幾年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the nearest ones, it takes years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,其他那些  幾百年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For others, centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一些特別遠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some stars are so far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,需要億萬年才能到達地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it takes eons for their light to get to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等那些星星發出的光到達這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the time the light from some stars gets here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,星星已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對這些星星來說  我們看到的只是他們的鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those stars, we see only their ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們看到他們的光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We see their light,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們的星球已經死了很久很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but their bodies perished long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰  我比我們的古人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John, I have seen further back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到更古老的過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than any man before me--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,幾百萬年前的過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}millions of years into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·赫歇爾是第一個認識到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}William Herschel was the first person to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,望遠鏡就是一個時間機器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that a telescope is a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們看向太空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot look out into space
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是看向過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without seeing back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一秒鐘  光穿越30萬公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In one second, light travels 300,000 kilometers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或者18萬6千英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or 186,000 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎就是地球到月亮的距離\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's nearly the distance from the Earth to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以月亮離我們1光秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, the Moon is about one light-second away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下次你看向月亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next time you look at the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會看到1秒鐘以前的過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll be seeing one second into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,中文翻譯：@SaltyEggPain
